MdePkg/Include/Uefi.h File Reference

Detailed Description

Root include file for Mde Package UEFI, UEFI_APPLICATION type modules.

This is the include file for any module of type UEFI and UEFI_APPLICATION. Uefi modules only use types defined via this include file and can be ported easily to any environment.
